WEBVTT

00:04:29.001 --> 00:04:31.031
the human rights organization,

00:04:31.055 --> 00:04:35.391
reports that 2015 marks
the 10th straight year in a row

00:04:35.415 --> 00:04:38.471
of decline in freedom worldwide.

00:04:38.495 --> 00:04:40.891
And this is not just
because of the actions

00:04:40.915 --> 00:04:42.946
of authoritarian governments.

00:04:42.970 --> 00:04:45.467
It's also because democratic governments

00:04:45.491 --> 00:04:49.794
are increasingly cracking
down on dissenters,

00:04:49.818 --> 00:04:50.986
whistle-blowers

00:04:51.010 --> 00:04:52.923
and investigative journalists.

00:04:52.947 --> 00:04:55.381
UN Secretary General
Ban Ki-Moon has warned

00:04:55.405 --> 00:04:59.842
that "preventing extremism and promoting
human rights go hand-in-hand."

00:04:59.866 --> 00:05:02.670
It's not to say that governments
shouldn't keep us safe --